testtool.models.questiondb

Class QuestionEntry

  • java.lang.Object
    • testtool.models.questiondb.QuestionEntry

  • public class QuestionEntry
extends java.lang.Object
    Version:
    20apr14 QuestionEntry is a modified version of a Question, that adds a boolean and an int to help manage QuestionList interactions. The component selected is for determining if a Question is selected, and the filtered value keeps track of whether or not the entry has been filtered out by a filter. More details to come later.
    Author:
    Neil Nordhof (nnordhof@calpoly.edu)
